---
<section id="problem" class="py-24 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 relative transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="reveal-left">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Most Online Courses Never Get Launched. <span class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">We Change That.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg">Overwhelmed by curriculum planning and content structure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg">Struggling with the technical setup of Kajabi or other LMS platforms.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg">Frustrated by low student engagement and completion rates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-12 reveal-right transition-colors duration-300">
        <div class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-bold text-5xl mb-4">90%</div>
        <div class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-xl font-bold mb-2">of self-paced courses are never finished.</div>
        <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">We help you build courses that students actually complete, using proven instructional design frameworks and interactive elements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
